  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Culture`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the preservation of ancient and historical monuments and archaeological sites and remains of national importance, for the regulation of archaeological excavations and for the protection of sculptures, carvings and other like objects.`)
